cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses a new stochastic training method for deep neural networks and its performance on image classification tasks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to machine learning and computer vision, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper proposes a new parameterization that reveals connections to existing architectures, which could also place it in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
